data.description: We are not some fancy place with a 'courtyard' theme - We are an actual courtyard turned into a cafe. We're located right on the main road but pretty well hidden. We're spacious, open, calm and laid back. Music, if at all is mostly retro, some blues and jazz. We're more than just good food and beverage; It's possible to sit back and enjoy a conversation or just be.
